A Steam update was released yesterday. When you exit and restart Steam, the following changes will take effect.<br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><li>update news for games is now always shown when first launching the new version</li><br/><li>fixed case where connecting to third-party mods via the server browser would launch cstrike instead</li><br/><li>fixed login dialog items staying disabled after login attempt failed with a network connection error</li><br/><li>fixed user interface #strings being displayed instead of the intended text</li><br/></ul><br/></p>
